To go #seedless organic or #seeded non organic that is the question‼️🤔...
Ppl ask me this all the time & I do recommend opting for organic whenever possible as the soil & roots play a major factor in the lifeforce, quality, & nutrients of the food‼️🔑...
But if I ever make an exception to that rule, it is with something with a hard shell like a #watermelon‼️🍉 ...
I definitely try to not make a habit out of it, but what’s more aggresious is non organic leafy greens & herbs thy don’t have a shell & the pesticide may be applied directly to the leaf‼️🙃...
Look into the “#dirtydozen “ & “ #clean15” “ for more perspective on what produce is more pesticide ridden than others‼️👁...
We’ll talk about the misconceptions of #organic & difference between organic & #conventional in a future post‼️🔑...
